  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/551eb0533b220e9ae6d2bcb4b56c346b.poster.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/551eb0533b220e9ae6d2bcb4b56c346b.webm?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/551eb0533b220e9ae6d2bcb4b56c346b.mp4?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take down numerous monsters and defeat boss monsters with your colleagues to obtain resources in the area you crossed through the portal! Portal Survivors is a casual game with rogue-lite elements. By combining your colleagues' occupations, skills, and magic characteristics delivered to the area you pass through the portal, you can kill a huge number of monsters in a variety of ways.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Portal Survivor Features </strong></h2></li></ul><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colleague</li></ul>Choose companions with a variety of skills and unique skills to make a party <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/7b1e87414ab218e084dca22b6ed0800d.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>After making a party with colleagues, take the portal and start the battle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/aa98d5e3d10ec84da0cce0217376c9e9.poster.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/aa98d5e3d10ec84da0cce0217376c9e9.webm?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/aa98d5e3d10ec84da0cce0217376c9e9.mp4?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Skills and Magic</li></ul>You can choose to grow your companion's skills and magic by leveling them up through experience points gained through battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/88eb25cf2b3d5c01f9c3a37b1f7ebf0e.poster.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/88eb25cf2b3d5c01f9c3a37b1f7ebf0e.webm?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/88eb25cf2b3d5c01f9c3a37b1f7ebf0e.mp4?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Town</li></ul>You can manage your adventure group’s abilities, quests, skill trees, etc.!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/f75d47b769895f138105c360ead9d503.poster.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/f75d47b769895f138105c360ead9d503.webm?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/f75d47b769895f138105c360ead9d503.mp4?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Through the Portal. and Survive!</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/2787907cfe6b8f13e7f1a98e811577ca.poster.avif?t=1707876103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/2787907cfe6b8f13e7f1a98e811577ca.webm?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/2787907cfe6b8f13e7f1a98e811577ca.mp4?t=1707876103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793300/extras/609bc6792b83966468c4ed662e87825a.avif?t=1707876103\" width=616 height=353 /></span>",
